DataTypes_key2: Aapne Javscript mein 4 tarah ke Data Types padhe:
DataTypes_key7: javascript mein *typeof* ka use karke aap kisi bhi `variable` ya data ka type pata laga sakte hain.
DataTypes_key8: Aap ek data type ko doosre data type mein convert bhi kar sakte hain. Iske liye javascript mein pehle se pre-defined methods
DataTypes_key14: parseInt() ka use karke `string` data "25" ko number mein convert karein. `Output` ko `variable` mein store karein aur *typeof* use karke check karein ki data type change hua ya nahi
DataTypes_key15: .to`String`() ka use karke number data 51 ko `string` mein convert karein. `Output` ko `variable` mein store karein aur *typeof* use karke check karein ki data type change hua ya nahi.
